Name: A Walk With My Dog
About the game: I have digitized my dog so we can go on walks forever and you can join us too! This is a short and peaceful walking simulator, inspired by real life. In This Game You Can: Pet the dog! Play fetch & tug of war with our dog Discover photos Put things in your backpack Explore the map And also relax and enjoy the sounds of nature
